# Prerequisites

To build this formalization, you will need Isabelle (tested with Isabelle2024: https://isabelle.in.tum.de/) and the Archive of Formal Proofs (https://www.isa-afp.org/download/)

# Build instructions

To build, from the folder that host the ROOT file, run:

isabelle build -d . -d /path/to/afp/thys -v Term_Indexing
